metadata.name: Buttery Boiled Lobster
metadata.description:
Buttery Boiled Lobster
 
The perfect dish to satisfy any hungry NFT connoisseur with an exceptional palate.
 
The succulent taste of this whole boiled lobster is complimented nicely by the accompanying clarified garlic butter resting on the side.
 
Clams steamed to perfection, as well as grilled corn on the cob, enhance the dining experience while a side salad and lemon help to balance the meal.
 
And of courseâ€¦ no lobster dinner is complete without a glass of our finest Chardonnay.
 
Side Note: Do be careful and watch your fingers, as this lobster does seem to be a bit feisty!

Digital Animation
Design Process: Illustrated using iPad Pro and ProCreate. Animated using Adobe After Effects
